## CSS

```css
/* =============================================
   c-button — Atom
   Layer: component (c-*)
   ============================================= */

.c-button {
  /* Layout & sizing */
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: var(--space-2);
  padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
  border: 2px solid transparent;
  border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
  cursor: pointer;

  /* Typography */
  font-family: var(--font-family-sans);
  font-size: var(--font-size-body);
  font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
  line-height: var(--line-height-base);

  /* Visual */
  background-color: transparent;
  color: inherit;
  text-decoration: none;
  white-space: nowrap;

  /* Motion */
  transition:
    background-color var(--transition-fast),
    color var(--transition-fast),
    border-color var(--transition-fast),
    box-shadow var(--transition-fast);

  /* Accessibility */
  user-select: none;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
  appearance: none;
}

/* =============================================
   Variants — via data-variant attribute
   ============================================= */

/* Primary */
.c-button[data-variant="primary"] {
  background-color: var(--color-background-brand);
  color: var(--color-text-on-brand);
  border-color: var(--color-background-brand);
}
.c-button[data-variant="primary"]:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--color-background-brand-hover);
  border-color: var(--color-background-brand-hover);
}
.c-button[data-variant="primary"]:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-border-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Secondary */
.c-button[data-variant="secondary"] {
  background-color: var(--color-background-secondary);
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  border-color: var(--color-border-default);
}
.c-button[data-variant="secondary"]:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--color-gray-200);
  border-color: var(--color-gray-400);
}
.c-button[data-variant="secondary"]:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-border-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Outline */
.c-button[data-variant="outline"] {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--color-brand-600);
  border-color: var(--color-brand-600);
}
.c-button[data-variant="outline"]:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--color-brand-50);
  color: var(--color-brand-700);
  border-color: var(--color-brand-700);
}
.c-button[data-variant="outline"]:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-border-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Ghost */
.c-button[data-variant="ghost"] {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--color-text-link);
  border-color: transparent;
}
.c-button[data-variant="ghost"]:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--color-gray-100);
  color: var(--color-text-link-hover);
}
.c-button[data-variant="ghost"]:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--color-border-focus);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* =============================================
   States — via data-state attribute
   ============================================= */

/* Loading */
.c-button[data-state="loading"] {
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.7;
}
.c-button[data-state="loading"] .c-button__label {
  visibility: hidden;
}
.c-button[data-state="loading"] .c-button__spinner {
  display: inline-flex;
  position: absolute;
}

/* Disabled */
.c-button[data-state="disabled"],
.c-button:disabled {
  opacity: 0.4;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Error */
.c-button[data-state="error"] {
  background-color: var(--color-background-error);
  color: var(--color-text-on-brand);
  border-color: var(--color-border-error);
  animation: c-button-shake var(--transition-base) ease-in-out;
}
.c-button[data-state="error"]:hover:not(:disabled) {
  background-color: var(--color-red-800);
  border-color: var(--color-red-800);
}

/* =============================================
   Sub-elements
   ============================================= */

.c-button__label {
  display: inline-block;
}

.c-button__spinner {
  display: none;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

/* =============================================
   Keyframes
   ============================================= */

@keyframes c-button-shake {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
  20% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
  40% { transform: translateX(4px); }
  60% { transform: translateX(-4px); }
  80% { transform: translateX(4px); }
}
```

---

## Design Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|
| **No margin on root** | Follows the Golden Rule — spacing is delegated to layout classes (`l-stack`, `l-cluster`). |
| **Variants via `data-variant`** | Keeps the class name clean and allows dynamic switching without class manipulation. |
| **States via `data-state`** | Aligns with MCSS state management rules — no class modifiers for state. |
| **Loading state uses `position: absolute` spinner** | Prevents layout shift when the label is hidden. |
| **Error state includes shake animation** | Provides immediate, accessible feedback without relying on color alone. |
| **All values use `var(--token)`** | Zero magic numbers — fully token-driven for theming and consistency. |
| **RDFa annotations** | Declares taxonomy level (`mcs:Atom`), purpose, interaction type, and custom event for machine readability. |

