}

.c-dropdown__item[data-state="active"] {
  background: var(--color-brand-100);
  color: var(--color-brand-700);
}

/* Arrow indicator */
.c-dropdown__arrow {
  transition: transform var(--transition-fast);
}

.c-dropdown[data-state="open"] .c-dropdown__arrow {
  transform: rotate(180deg);
}
```

## Event Flow

```
User clicks trigger
  → JavaScript checks current data-state
  → Toggles data-state (open ↔ closed)
  → Updates aria-expanded (true ↔ false)
  → Dispatches custom event: mcss:dropdown:toggled
  → CSS transitions apply based on new state
  → Focus management (if opening, focus first item)
```

## Composition (Molecule Structure)

```html
<div typeof="mcs:Component" property="mcs:taxonomyLevel" content="mcs:Molecule">
  <!-- Trigger (Atom) -->
  <button 
    typeof="mcs:Component" 
    property="mcs:taxonomyLevel" content="mcs:Atom"
    property="mcs:hasPart" resource="#dropdown-trigger"
    class="c-dropdown__trigger"
  >
    <span class="c-dropdown__label">Options</span>
    <svg class="c-dropdown__arrow" aria-hidden="true">...</svg>
  </button>

  <!-- Menu (Atom) -->
  <ul 
    typeof="mcs:Component"
    property="mcs:taxonomyLevel" content="mcs:Atom"
